{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/general-fizzbuzz","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"FizzBuzz uopšteno","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Napiši opštu verziju od <a href=\"https://rosettacode.org/wiki/FizzBuzz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">FizzBuzz</a> koja radi za bilo koju listu parametara, zajedno sa njihovim vrednostima.</p>\n<p>Ovo je implementacija \"fizzbuzz\"-a gde su pravila igre data korisniku. Napravi funkciju koja ovo izvršava. Funkcija treba da primi dva parametra.</p>\n<p>Prvi test će biti red podataka sa pravilima FizzBuzz-a. Na primer: <code>[ [3, \"Fizz\"] , [5, \"Buzz\"] ]</code>.</p>\n<p>Ovo pokazuje da <code>Fizz</code> treba da se ispruša ako je broj često 3 i <code>Buzz</code> ako je često 5. Ako je često oba, onda se niz slova treba kombinovati u redosledu definisanom u redu podataka. U ovom slučaju, <code>FizzBuzz</code> ako je broj često 3 i 5.</p>\n<p>Drugi kriterijum je broj koji funkcija mora vratiti sekvencu karaktera, kao što je opisano iznad.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc7e78","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302273,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/general-fizzbuzz"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function genFizzBuzz(rules, num) {\n\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz</code> trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof genFizzBuzz == 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Fizz\"],[5, \"Buzz\"]], 6)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu slova.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  typeof genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Fizz'],\n      [5, 'Buzz']\n    ],\n    6\n  ) == 'string'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Fizz\"],[5, \"Buzz\"]], 6)</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Fizz\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Fizz'],\n      [5, 'Buzz']\n    ],\n    6\n  ),\n  'Fizz'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Fizz\"],[5, \"Buzz\"]], 10)</code> treba da vrati <code>\"Buzz\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Fizz'],\n      [5, 'Buzz']\n    ],\n    10\n  ),\n  'Buzz'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Buzz\"],[5, \"Fizz\"]], 12)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>\"Buzz\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Buzz'],\n      [5, 'Fizz']\n    ],\n    12\n  ),\n  'Buzz'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Buzz\"],[5, \"Fizz\"]], 13)</code> treba da vrati <code>\"13\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Buzz'],\n      [5, 'Fizz']\n    ],\n    13\n  ),\n  '13'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Buzz\"],[5, \"Fizz\"]], 15)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>\"BuzzFizz\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Buzz'],\n      [5, 'Fizz']\n    ],\n    15\n  ),\n  'BuzzFizz'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Fizz\"],[5, \"Buzz\"]], 15)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>\"FizzBuzz\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Fizz'],\n      [5, 'Buzz']\n    ],\n    15\n  ),\n  'FizzBuzz'\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>genFizzBuzz([[3, \"Fizz\"],[5, \"Buzz\"],[7, \"Baxx\"]], 105)</code> bi trebalo da vrati <code>\"FizzBuzzBaxx\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  genFizzBuzz(\n    [\n      [3, 'Fizz'],\n      [5, 'Buzz'],\n      [7, 'Baxx']\n    ],\n    105\n  ),\n  'FizzBuzzBaxx'\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"general-fizzbuzz","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/generate-lower-case-ascii-alphabet","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/gaussian-elimination","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc7e78","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/general-fizzbuzz"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}